25
00:03:07,201 --> 00:03:10,239
- Šta može ovaj lepotan? 130?
- 140.

26
00:03:10,442 --> 00:03:12,797
Probaj 150.

27
00:03:13,003 --> 00:03:15,153
Balaviš nad mojim poklonom za maturu.

28
00:03:15,363 --> 00:03:17,274
- Tvoja matura?
- Tako je.

29
00:03:17,483 --> 00:03:21,272
- Gde si ga nabavio?
- Kako misliš nabavio?

30
00:03:21,484 --> 00:03:23,043
- Lagao? Varao?
- Ukrao?

31
00:03:23,245 --> 00:03:28,240
- Dovezao ga je iz svoje garaže.
- Jel ovo faca lažova?

32
00:03:28,446 --> 00:03:30,198
Da!

33
00:03:31,366 --> 00:03:32,720
Ne!

34
00:03:33,447 --> 00:03:36,598
