73
00:08:20,225 --> 00:08:22,785
Sranje!

74
00:08:28,707 --> 00:08:31,779
Naravno, izvinite! Oprostite mi.

75
00:08:33,988 --> 00:08:37,219
- Hvala vam, Gospodine, srećno.
- Hvala.

76
00:08:37,428 --> 00:08:39,863
U redu, krećemo!

77
00:08:45,950 --> 00:08:48,465
- OK, idemo.
- Stavite ih ovde...

78
00:09:06,714 --> 00:09:09,388
- Završeno za danas?
- Eh da je.

79
00:09:09,595 --> 00:09:12,906
- Izvinite, samo napred.
- Hvala.

80
00:09:14,916 --> 00:09:18,114
Bože, što ste lepi!

81
00:09:18,317 --> 00:09:20,911
Izvinite, nekako mi se omaklo.

82
00:09:21,117 --> 00:09:25,077
Ne mislim da ste rekli
bog zna šta.

83
00:09:26,478 --> 00:09:30,916
Koja je kao takva
neverovatno iskrena.

84
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:35,920
Pokopala me!

85
00:09:37,761 --> 00:09:40,355
Dobar pokušaj, momak.

86
00:09:54,684 --> 00:09:58,155
- Šta gledaš ti?
- Ništa.

87
00:09:58,365 --> 00:10:00,754
Ništa.

88
00:10:00,965 --> 00:10:03,719
Onda tako nastavi.

89
00:10:10,647 --> 00:10:13,526
I ovaj me pokopao.

90
00:10:13,728 --> 00:10:18,359
Pa, šta vam je zadovoljstvo, Gospodine?
Kocka, rulet, blek džek...

91
00:10:18,569 --> 00:10:22,768
Imate li poker ovde?

92
00:10:24,250 --> 00:10:26,047
Tri desetke.

93
00:10:27,451 --> 00:10:30,204
Ti si na potezu, Deni.

94
00:10:30,411 --> 00:10:33,802
- Može li ovaj gospodin da vam se pridruži?
- Naravno.

95
00:10:35,532 --> 00:10:37,683
Zdravo, ja sam Čarli.

96
00:10:37,893 --> 00:10:40,965
- Ono je Hal, Bob...
- Zdravo, Čarli.

97
00:10:41,173 --> 00:10:43,642
...Barbara, Deni.

98
00:10:44,894 --> 00:10:46,248
Deni.

99
00:10:47,135 --> 00:10:49,603
Dolarski ulog, pošten poker,
ništa divlje,

100
